data.description: Stunning 3-bed, 3.5-bath TH nestled in the highly sought-after Lakelands community offering huge savings via remarkably low 2.25% VA loan that can be assumed by VA eligible buyers. This vibrant home greets you with cork flooring and a generously sized entry-level bedroom with French doors, window shutters and an upgraded full bath (2017), featuring a beautifully tiled walk-in shower. Ascend to the bright and airy main level with wide plank white oak hardwood floors throughout. Chef’s kitchen boasts gorgeous wood cabinets, stainless steel appliances, granite countertops, recessed lighting, two-tier island with bar seating and breakfast area. Entertain guests in the adjacent dining area or cozy up by the gas fireplace in the large family room, overlooking the private deck, perfect for enjoying your morning coffee. Convenient main-level powder room. When ready to unwind, head upstairs to the large owner's suite with two walk-in closets and upgraded spa-like bath (2017), including dual-sink vanity, tiled floors, and oversized stand-up shower with frameless glass door and shower bench. An additional generously sized bedroom with vaulted ceiling, full bath with tub/shower combo, and laundry room complete the upper level. Recent improvements include HVAC damper and ductwork (2020), Roof (2022), and HVAC (2012). Attached 2 car garage plus driveway. Enjoy the endless community amenities including outdoor pool, sports courts, walking paths, playgrounds and more! Just .5 miles to Downtown Kentlands with Whole Foods, Starbucks, Cinepolis, and many dining options. Close to RIO, Crown and I-270. Rachel Carson ES, Lakelands MS and Quince Orchard HS districts. Don’t miss this rare find!
